// CollapsibleMarkdown
// Wraps a full markdown document into collapsible H2/H3 sections.
// Splits the markdown source on heading boundaries and renders each section
// as a CollapsibleDetails block so long documents are easier to navigate.

FUNCTION CollapsibleMarkdown(content, components) -> JSX               EXPORT
  CALLS: CollapsibleDetails (CollapsibleDetails)
  Parses content into sections by splitting on H2/H3 headings.
  First section (before any heading) rendered as plain markdown.
  Each subsequent section rendered as a CollapsibleDetails with the heading as
  the summary and the remaining text as the body.
  Passes components overrides into each ReactMarkdown instance.
